videos.description: Ronald Jones II run for 61 yds to the Cal 27 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: R. Jones II run for 61 yds for a 1ST down

videos.description: Sam Darnold pass complete to Darreus Rogers for 3 yds for a TD
videos.headline: S. Darnold pass to D. Rogers for 3 yds for a TD

videos.description: USC shows off how to execute the perfect screen pass, which ends up with Ronald Jones II ending a 95-yard drive with seven points and a 14-0 lead over California.
videos.headline: USC executes the perfect screen pass for 16-yard touchdown

videos.description: Davis Webb pass intercepted Marvell Tell III return for no gain to the USC 7
videos.headline: D. Webb pass intercepted, M. Tell III return for 0 yds

videos.description: USC is starting to run away from Cal when Sam Darnold hits Deontay Burnett for his third touchdown pass of the game, this one from 13 yards out to put the Trojans ahead 21-0.
videos.headline: Darnold hits Burnett for third TD pass of the game

videos.description: Sam Darnold sacked by DeVante Wilson for 0 yards to the Cal 42 Sam Darnold fumbled, recovered by Cal James Looney , return for 0 yards
videos.headline: Cal forces USC fumble

videos.description: After recovering a fumble in USC territory, Cal converts the turnover into points in just three plays when Davis Webb finds Tre Watson from 22 yards out to cut into USC's lead at 21-7.
videos.headline: Cal strikes back quickly off turnover to cut in to USC's lead

videos.description: Sam Darnold finishes a monster first half with his fourth touchdown pass of the game, this time hitting Darreus Rogers from 20 yards out to increase the Trojans' lead to 28-10.
videos.headline: Darnold makes it four TD passes in just the first half

videos.description: Davis Webb pass complete to Melquise Stovall for 3 yds Melquise Stovall fumbled, forced by Uchenna Nwosu, recovered by USC Ajene Harris
videos.headline: D. Webb pass,to M. Stovall for 3 yds,M. Stovall fumbled, forced by U. Nwosu, recovered by USC A. Harris

videos.description: Davis Webb run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: D. Webb runs for 1-yard TD

videos.description: Ronald Jones II takes the handoff, gets through a tackle and then turns on the jets to race 37 yards into the end zone boosting USC's lead to 35-17.
videos.headline: Jones finds daylight and bursts to the end zone for 37-yard USC TD

videos.description: Sam Darnold's massive night continues as he throws his fifth touchdown, this one to Daniel Imatorbhebhe from 17 yards out, to push the USC lead to 42-17 over Cal.
videos.headline: Darnold makes it five TDs as USC continues to roll

videos.description: Davis Webb pass complete to Melquise Stovall for 16 yds for a TD
videos.headline: D. Webb pass to M. Stovall for 16 yds for a TD

videos.description: Sam Darnold pass intercepted Luke Rubenzer return for 27 yds to the Cal 30
videos.headline: S. Darnold pass intercepted, L. Rubenzer return  for 27 yds
